'Explain yourself , says the mother , 'for I am surprised I do not understand you . 
I hope you are not in earnest . 
Here the sisters put in . 
Robin was a little warmed with his sister's rudeness , but he was even with her , and yet with good manners too . 
The younger sister then put in . 
'Answer , and answer not , say Solomon , replied her brother . 
'My mother , you see , did not understand it , says the second sister . 
'There's some difference , says Robin , 'between desiring me to explain it , and telling me she did not believe it . 
I hope my warm sisters will be answered now , and blush a little if not , I have no more to say till I hear further . 
This answer was surprising to them all , though less to the mother , because of what I had said to her . 
'Nay , says the eldest sister , 'if it be so , she has acted handsomely indeed . 
'But I shall not , says Robin , 'unless you will give your consent . 
But this I will say , I am in earnest in , that I will never have anybody else if I can help it so you may determine for me . 
All this was dreadful to me , for the mother began to yield , and Robin pressed her home on it . 
Then he told the whole story between Robin , as he called him , and his mother and sisters and himself , as it is above . 
On the other hand , he failed not to set forth the easy , prosperous life which I was going to live . 
I should go back a little here to where I left off . 
So certainly does interest banish all manner of affection , and so naturally do men give up honour and justice , humanity , and even Christianity , to secure themselves . 
My two children were , indeed , taken happily off my hands by my husband's father and mother , and that , by the way , was all they got by Mrs. Betty . 
Before my husband died his elder brother was married , and we , being then removed to London , were written to by the old lady to come and be at the wedding . 
As for their common design , that I understood too well to be drawn into any more snares of that kind . 
The case was altered with me I had money in my pocket , and had nothing to say to them . 
On the other hand , those who came with the best proposals were the dullest and most disagreeable part of the world . 
I said for myself , for I was not trepanned , I confess , but I betrayed myself . 
