I was not wicked enough for such fellows as these yet . 
On the contrary , I began to consider here very seriously what I had to do how things stood with me , and what course I ought to take . 
I had made an acquaintance with a very sober , good sort of a woman , who was a widow too , like me , but in better circumstances . 
Such as , having good business , that is to say , a good ship , resolved not to marry but with advantage , that is , with a good fortune . 
