With all these fine compliments we parted , and I came merry enough to London , and found my governess as well pleased as I was . 
From hence 'tis evident to me , that when once we are hardened in crime , no fear can affect us , no example give us any warning . 
I had indeed one comrade whose fate went very near me for a good while , though I wore it off too in time . 
